imdb.plot: The Republic of San Magnolia is at war with its neighboring country, the Empire of Giad. Both sides use unmanned drones to conduct a "war without casualties". The story follows Lena as she commands a squad of drones called the 86.

episodes.title: Welcome
episodes.plot: After being demoted, Lena is now the handler of a different squadron of Eighty-Six, and with the words left behind by Shin, she prepares for the large scale offensive of the Legion that she believes will come.

episodes.title: It's Too Late
episodes.plot: The remaining members of Spearhead settle into their new life in the Federacy of Giad.

episodes.title: Glad To Be Here
episodes.plot: Shin and his squad enlist in the Special Officer School where Shin trains with Eugene.

episodes.title: Welcome Back
episodes.plot: After the Nordlicht squadron was split up to help the various mechanized infantry divisions, they are finally reunited to prepare for another large looming threat.

episodes.title: Even So
episodes.plot: The Nordlicht squadron takes to the front lines as the Legion's large scale invasion begins.

episodes.title: I Won't Forget
episodes.plot: Lena takes command of the 86 as the fighting gets closer to the capital. The Federacy of Giad deals with the aftermath from the attacks from the Railgun Legion, now dubbed "The Morpho"

episodes.title: The Truth is
episodes.plot: To assist in reaching their objective, the Nordlicht squadron sets out in a forgotten prototype, as the the Federacy, the Kingdom of Roa Gracia, and the Alliance of Wald simultaneously begin their massive assault against the Legion forces.

episodes.title: Stay This Way Forever
episodes.plot: The Nachzehrer finds its flight path blocked by a massive swam of Legion before they could reach their landing point and the bulk of Nordlicht are ejected from the plane. Grethe baits the Legion away as the rest push on towards the Morpho.

episodes.title: Together Unto Death
episodes.plot: As they continue to go deeper into Legion territory in pursuit of the Morpho, Shin is confronted by Raiden about his actions during the previous skirmish. The rest of the Federacy's forces follow close behind.

episodes.title: All That's Left
episodes.plot: As the Eighty-Six approaches the Morpho, the path is repeatedly blocked by attacks from the Legion. In order to advance, they each take on the role of decoys, and their numbers are dwindling one by one.

episodes.title: Shin
episodes.plot: After the war, Shin confronts himself as the only one left behind on the battlefield. Just before giving up, he is approached by a figure from his past.

episodes.title: Handler One
episodes.plot: Shin and his squadron return from the front lines to celebrate, to find to find that they will be reorganized under under a new commanding officer.

episodes.title: Undertaker
episodes.plot: Stellar Year 2148, Major Vladilena is forced to take the lead of District 86. Rumors say that whoever was it's Head, they ended up resigning or committing suicide. Vladilena does not believe it and wants to investigate.

episodes.title: Spearhead
episodes.plot: As Lena lives a life of safety and comfort inside the walls of her city, the 86 fight a terrible battle against an unstoppable and inhuman enemy.

episodes.title: I Don't Want to Die
episodes.plot: Lena finds herself growing closer to the Spearhead squadron, or so she thinks. However a deadly battle drastically changes her perspective.

episodes.title: Real Name
episodes.plot: After a brutal death, Lena comes to terms with her real status as an Alba, and what it means to force another to fight for your sake.

episodes.title: I'm With You
episodes.plot: Lena learns the truth about the upcoming end of the war, and how the Legion is a much more deadly threat than she thought.

episodes.title: Through to the End
episodes.plot: Spearhead enjoys a brief respite near the cherry blossoms outside the wall, but a deadly attack brings the dangers of war even closer to home.

episodes.title: Will You Remember Me?
episodes.plot: As the day of the festival arrives, Lena and Shin watch the fireworks and enjoy a brief respite from their battles.

episodes.title: Let's Go
episodes.plot: Spearhead is given orders to undertake a pointless march into enemy territory, and not to stop until they are dead. Lena tries her best to stop this suicide mission from happening.

episodes.title: Goodbye
episodes.plot: Shin confronts his brother deep within Legion held territory. But even if he wins, there's no going back.

episodes.title: Thank You
episodes.plot: After the climactic battle, the 86 move through unknown territory, finally free from war and the Republic.

episodes.title: Here We Go
episodes.plot: With pride in themselves and a vow to their fallen comrades, they will not stop until the end. And so, they reach their final resting place. Meanwhile, Lena, who was left behind in the Republic, finally landed on their land.

episodes.title: Special Edition: The Poppies Bloom Red on the Battlefield
episodes.plot: Recap of the first eleven episodes.
